description.en-us:
Truckin' Transporters was the third series of transport trucks which included bonus vehicles.
The series ran from 2003 to 2008, being replaced by Racing Rigs . Note: International packaging for 2011 and 2012 Racing Rigs used the Truckin' Transporters name.
